Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Endpoint Engineer position with SCAN Health Plan. I bring over three years of professional experience in automation, endpoint management, and systems engineering, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

