I have always been passionate about improving care for older adults and building systems that strengthen mission-driven organizations, and I deeply resonate with SCAN's commitment to keeping seniors healthy and independent through innovation, accountability, and respect for the communities you serve. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

